events.name: Amped Up
events.description: Come meet the brothers of Nu Delta at our beautiful Boston 4 story mansion. Stick around and get house tours, play some video games, pool, fuse ball, and much more. Challenge and defeat the most brothers and you'll walk away with a fabulous prize!

events.name: JET SKIS
events.description: An afternoon on the beach, Jet Skiing, and Nu Delt bros? Doesn't get much better than that!

events.name: Paintball
events.description: An evening of indoor painball right before the Party Bus is a great start to a looong night!

events.name: Firing Range
events.description: Test your aim with a set of different rifles and handguns. Beginner or expert, this is a thrilling (and safe) event for everyone

events.name: SkyZone
events.description: Your backyard trampoline has nothing on this experience. Dodgeball, basketball, back flips and more!

events.name: Steak & Lobster
events.description: Prime steak and fresh caught lobster. A hearty meal is definitely a necessity before Monster Jam tonight!

events.name: Target Runs
events.description: We'll take 2 separate trips to Target to make sure we all have all the supplies for the coming semester. Give us a call for a ride.

events.name: Dick's Last Resort
events.description: Things get pretty rowdy whenever Nu Delts show up to Dick's Last Resort. Take a night out to celebrate your first classes at MIT!

events.name: SK Late Night
events.description: Come down to Sigma Kappa and watch ND throw down in a talent show against some of the other MIT fraternities!  It's always a great show, so make sure not to miss it!

events.name: The D is far dance
events.description: Come challenge the brothers of Nu Delta to Just dance! Food and drink will be served.

events.name: ND Lounging
events.description: Want to party tonight? We'll be ready to party hop with you. Or maybe you'd just like to take the night off until the real party at Nu Delta tomorrow(SIKE, not happening anymore)? Either way, come meet and chill with the brothers of Nu Delta at our house. There will be delicious chicken wings, good music, games, and more to go round!

events.name: Tex-Mex Breakast
events.description: Swing by Nu Delta for an amazing Tex-Mex style breakfast with chorizo & eggs, chilaquiles, and breakfast tacos/burritos. And BACON!!!

events.name: Nu Smoothies
events.description: All partied out tonight? Looking for something to eat? Stop by Nu Delta on your way home to close out the night with snacks and some next level smoothies.

events.name: Breakfast of Champions
events.description: Rise From The Ashes of last night's parties with a Breakfast Of Champions at Nu Delta. 460 Beacon ST. Guaranteed to be delicious.
